{"tid":1760645,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 有方法攞到立法會飲食界個位","createTime":"2019-11-28T10:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T08:19:30.000Z","uid":189799,"like":110,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"57ee5d31ad401d17de442d2ecddb43b3afb83128","tid":1760645,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:53:58.000Z","msg":"2016年立法會<br />\n張宇人得票2438<br />\n伍永德得票647<br />\n兩者相差1791票<br />\n根據2017年資料，現時飲食界有5013張選票。<br />\n下年可以點攞多1791票呢。<br />\n睇落好似好難，但留意番，我地有個好好嘅工具。<br />\n就是<span style=\"color: red;\">黃藍地圖，和你eat</span>喱啲教你搵黃店嘅工具。<br />\n我地去黃店食野嘅時間，說服黃店老闆登記做飲食界選民。同時搵多啲app入面無嘅黃店，重點遊說。<br />\n成件事好簡單，幫襯多啲黃店，變熟客，說服老闆登記做選民。（留意番持牌人先可以投）"},{"pid":"bcd435e3fac3428e249d99ce064252a8b7af72e5","tid":1760645,"uid":8301,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"唔好幫襯藍店，令佢地執粒，變相少左對家選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f42d3e3c244a1dab00cbccb7363da1b1885b6d","tid":1760645,"uid":189799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"如何成為[飲食界]工能界別選民：<br />\n1. 已登記為地方選區選民，或符合資格登記.<br />\n2. 根據《公眾衞生及市政條例》(第 132 章)發出的食物業牌照的持有人.<br />\n3. 請填寫表格 REO-41(&ldquo;功能界別選民及/或選舉委員會界別分 組投票人個人登記申請表&rdquo;)，申請登記在這個功能界別及一 個選舉委員會界別分組.<br />\n*個人地方選民新登記在7月2日截止.<br />\n<br />\nREO-41 表格 中文 <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtBBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=916eb7ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\nREO-41 form English <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28E&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtBBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=045c5952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(E</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n張REO-41可以郵遞方式寄回 九龍九龍灣展貿徑一號九龍灣國際展貿中心十三樓 / 傳真至 2891 1180<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n補番申請方法"},{"pid":"9532a2eef3672c4067e2de8df5f58abae612ade5","tid":1760645,"uid":209781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"1d295d06d0515a77219432a7c490cc2661f95e77","tid":1760645,"uid":72204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"依個必須推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add9ad3896f4cb3d672485c38f9aff897d618d78","tid":1760645,"uid":96226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:57:10.000Z","msg":"有用post 推"},{"pid":"5f6969363a8460e1f7ec0df655d1a62930400c1b","tid":1760645,"uid":262428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57ee5d31ad401d17de442d2ecddb43b3afb83128","tid":1760645,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:53:58.000Z","msg":"2016年立法會<br />\n張宇人得票2438<br />\n伍永德得票647<br />\n兩者相差1791票<br />\n根據2017年資料，現時飲食界有5013張選票。<br />\n下年可以點攞多1791票呢。<br />\n睇落好似好難，但留意番，我地有個好好嘅工具。<br />\n就是<span style=\"color: red;\">黃藍地圖，和你eat</span>喱啲教你搵黃店嘅工具。<br />\n我地去黃店食野嘅時間，說服黃店老闆登記做飲食界選民。同時搵多啲app入面無嘅黃店，重點遊說。<br />\n成件事好簡單，幫襯多啲黃店，變熟客，說服老闆登記做選民。（留意番持牌人先可以投）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:57:31.000Z","msg":"特別留意有啲情況下 幾間分店可以投幾票<br />\n一定唔好蝕底<br />\n攞到盡"},{"pid":"9e221998fe1fc1dff804cea6d75ad5c0b3ca7bff","tid":1760645,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"